{"tid":888933,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"青春vs成熟 點揀?","createTime":"2018-11-04T07:28:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T07:48:19.000Z","uid":66171,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bff6d422e4089fa16df9440b44a23fd45a2fe0a7","tid":888933,"uid":66171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T07:28:40.000Z","msg":"一個女仔<br />\n<br />\n普遍係青春少艾嘅時候都係只求開心 冇咁現實<br />\n但幼稚啲 要陪要氹<br />\n<br />\n相反係佢地踏入社會有更多歷練 個人亦會慢慢變得現實 感情未必係最重要考量 但想法同個性就成熟啲<br />\n<br />\n假設你係一個尋求長遠發展(視結婚為前提)嘅男人 點揀?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  =青春 冇咁現實 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  =成熟 冇咁幼稚<br />\n假設只存在呢2個對立case, 唔考慮 青春且成熟等嘅case<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9ee4db54367c8be4f85c74b9a7aa943fc2c8ce","tid":888933,"uid":62822,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T07:35:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee267c5fc6977228bbd0d27ee6866f625b6d3139","tid":888933,"uid":66171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e9ee4db54367c8be4f85c74b9a7aa943fc2c8ce","tid":888933,"uid":62822,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T07:35:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T07:36:14.000Z","msg":"同主題內容無關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dbfa5685a00c90835e8d34908658d54fc297536","tid":888933,"uid":103248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T07:41:11.000Z","msg":"睇你自已幾多歲wor<br />\n急住結婚咪成熟<br />\n仲後生就咁係青春...<br />\n拍幾年青春都變成熟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"587e2cf366650e0e9e4c8fa08d358814fd6b3df0","tid":888933,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T07:48:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8rTVgqK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8rTVgqK.png&h=65664fbb&s=